headline: TFI International Inc. (TFII) Q3 Earnings Beat Estimates
summary: TFI International (TFII) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +0.84% and -3.31%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
